Outlook: New and improved People Hub on Web

MC1199768 =C2=B7 MMC

Introduction

We=E2=80=99re introducing the new and improved People Hub in Outlook Web, d=
esigned to deliver a modern, multi-column contacts experience with fast sea=
rch and a streamlined interface. We=E2=80=99re investing in fast, relevant =
search and modern contact management capabilities that deliver a high-quali=
ty experience for everyone.

This update provides a unified view of each person, automatically links dup=
licate entries, and enriches contacts with organizational profile informati=
on where available. These enhancements aim to improve reliability and scala=
bility for organizations of all sizes, while phasing out older solutions th=
at no longer meet performance expectations.

